# https://bugs.gentoo.org/743938#c4 bubblewrap does not provide /sys
media-tv/kodi                       notest

# forces +X
dev-util/cmake                      notest

# You must have CONFIG_KEY_DH_OPERATIONS to run the package testsuite!
